node.title: Pedestrian dies after being hit by car in Taup≈ç
node.description: Police are asking the public for any sightings or dashcam footage.
node.content: ["A pedestrian has died after being struck by a car in Taup\u014d overnight.", "Police say emergency services responded to a serious crash involving a pedestrian and a car on Broadlands Rd shortly after 1:15am.", "Police are asking the public for any sightings or dashcam footage of a man walking on the road between midnight and 1:30am.", "Anyone with information should call 105 and quote job number P049046921.", "Information can also be passed on anonymously by contacting Crime Stoppers on 0800 555 111."]
